    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Of a person, or his or her feelings: estranged, excluded, or turned away (from a person or thing); experiencing a feeling of estrangement or isolation. Also in extended use: (of a period, place, etc.) characterized by or inducing such feelings.</Note_Text>
